# Import your ChatGPT/Claude history — bring your past into Brain.
# Render: npm run demo:render -- import-your-history
Output demos/out/import-your-history.gif
Output demos/out/import-your-history.mp4
Output demos/out/import-your-history.webm

Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1100
Set Height 760
Set Padding 24
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 35ms
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set WindowBarSize 36

Hide
Type "clear"
Enter
Show

Type "node demos/scripts/import-your-history.mjs"
Sleep 600ms
Enter
Sleep 22s
